<item>
            <title>[MSHADE-298] Groovy extension module transformer looking in incorrect META-INF directory</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MSHADE-298</link>
                <project id="12317921" key="MSHADE">Maven Shade Plugin (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Groovy extension module transformer seems to be looking in the incorrect META-INF directory for files to merge together.&#160; The code is looking&#160;for &lt;tt&gt;META-INF/services/org.codehaus.groovy.runtime.ExtensionModule&lt;/tt&gt;&#160; but the groovy documentation says to put the extension module files in&#160;&lt;tt&gt;META-INF/groovy&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1.8.4. Module descriptor&lt;br/&gt;
For Groovy to be able to load your extension methods, you must declare your extension helper classes. You must create a file named&#160;&lt;tt&gt;org.codehaus.groovy.runtime.ExtensionModule&lt;/tt&gt;&#160;into the&#160;&lt;tt&gt;META-INF/groovy&lt;/tt&gt;&#160;directory&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MSHADE-241&quot; title=&quot;Groovy extension module transformer&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MSHADE-241&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;MSHADE-241&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-plugins/pull/96/files&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/maven-plugins/pull/96/files&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://groovy-lang.org/metaprogramming.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://groovy-lang.org/metaprogramming.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s a minimal program to reproduce the issue.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/cogman/brokenshade&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/cogman/brokenshade&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
